videos.description: Texas Tech's Devon Thomas steals the ball and takes it to the hoop for a dunk.
videos.headline: Devon Thomas forces a steal and turns it into a dunk

videos.description: Texas Tech's Devon Thomas forces a steal and finds Zach Smith for the 2-handed finish on an alley-oop.
videos.headline: Thomas comes up with another steal that leads to an alley-oop slam

videos.description: Kansas State's Barry Brown and Wesley Iwundu get blocks on Texas Tech's Keenan Evans and Dean Wade hits a Kansas State 3-Pointer as a result.
videos.headline: Two Kansas State blocks lead to a 3-Pointer

videos.description: Texas Tech's Keenan Evans gets a steal then hits a lay-up to give Texas Tech a 63-62 lead with 14 seconds remaining.
videos.headline: Texas Tech takes a one point lead off a late steal

videos.description: Postgame Breakdown of Texas Tech's last minute 66-65 victory over Kansas State.
videos.headline: Breaking down Keenan Evans' second half performance in Texas Tech's 66-65 win against Kansas State

videos.description: Keenan Evans' layup with 15 seconds left puts Texas Tech up for good in a 66-65 win over No. 25 Kansas State.
videos.headline: Texas Tech holds off Kansas State
